***DISCLAIMER***

This game is a fan based game made from a fan

You are expected to find out what the cause of this entire creepy story is about, by yourself. Find easter eggs, think sharp, and most importantly, survive.
Now enjoy the all NEW multiplayer mode, which comes packed with usable animatronics of your choice, different maps, upgrades, live camera feed, interactive features on touch(door), and many more features soon to be added to multiplayer mode. You can choose any animatronic of your choice to impersonate, but only avaliable in multiplayer. You must have decent internet speed to enjoy gameplay.
